          <p class="text-slate-500 mb-4">Integrated systems that handle large storm events while protecting your foundation from water damage.</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-500 space-y-1">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-cyan-600">✓</span> 10" rainfall capacity</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-cyan-600">✓</span> Underground storage</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-cyan-600">✓</span> Overflow protection</li>
